{"tid":2381404,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中大推鐵欄撒粉案　被通緝中大生傍晚自首　至今5人被捕 (22:04)","createTime":"2021-01-26T14:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T02:51:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":31,"dislike":229,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff1359b5f0b962ac9fb4b87d1830c54a7686e31","tid":2381404,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"【21:57更新】1月11日為中大新學期開課日，約8名黑衣人於大學站外呼籲學生入校園時不必出示學生證，其後推跌鐵欄及向追截保安撒白色粉末，警方早前拘捕一名中大生涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢及普通襲擊。警方昨（25日）再拘捕3名中大生，涉非法集結及襲擊他人意圖導致不作出某些作為，當中包括中大學生會前會長區倬僖，今早（26日）表示正通緝餘下一名中大生。據悉，該22歲中大生傍晚到荃灣警署自首，涉嫌「非法集結」及「襲擊他人意圖導致不作出某些作為」被捕，現正被拘查，案件至今共5人被捕，全為中大學生。"},{"pid":"74924f4b3572b3ce0edce471f123f9813f7b3526","tid":2381404,"uid":76804,"like":98,"dislike":5,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T14:09:26.000Z","msg":"唔講以為d粉係砒霜黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e598dba87a5b6656f07eb695c55e9a3aeadab5","tid":2381404,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a30dec09c32ee9637b39b8ebfabe0b59b36c08","tid":2381404,"uid":155095,"like":96,"dislike":7,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"暴大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpYRT6kX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpYRT6kX.jpg&h=d21e8fdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84cb084a2564c4784631c949e4deca5c41af442b","tid":2381404,"uid":50890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,